    <string name="allowOnline_acceptMessage">
        By accepting you give consent to Utilities to save your Online CashBox data.
         This data will be saved anonymously with the username of your choice. Take into account
        that the data introduced may be lost, deleted or modified due to unexpected incidents.
        \nYou can withdraw you consent at any time disabling the \"Allow online mode\" option in Settings.
         By doing so, your user and all your saved data will be deleted from the server.
         The data shared with other users will remain being available to them, but will stop being
         linked to your user.
    </string>
